<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ample-adj">ample <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'æmpl/    美 /'æmpl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>足够的；充裕的：</strong></h4>
<p>more than enough:</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They gave him <strong>ample time</strong> to do this research.
他们给他充裕的时间来做这项研究。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 5</footer></div></div>